- Oddnes.

13
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:34,409
Dočerta aj s vami.

14
00:00:34,710 --> 00:00:37,380
Tak na mňa počkajte.

15
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:48,390
Pane, je vám teplo?

16
00:00:48,390 --> 00:00:49,890
Mám otvoriť okná?

17
00:00:50,689 --> 00:00:52,859
Prepáčte, pane.

18
00:00:52,859 --> 00:00:55,829
Ale bolo toho na mňa už priveľa.

19
