"Prichytení pri nevere"?

93
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,529
- "Yi Youngin priateľ"? 
- Ale nie.

94
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:26,060
Panebože.

95
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,930
- Čo to je? 
- Hong Yi Young?

96
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:30,399
- Hong Yi Young? 
- Už ide.

97
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:32,740
Skryte to.

98
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:44,779
Prečo je tu bezo mňa také ticho?

99
00:05:46,379 --> 00:05:48,250
Mali by sme piť.

100
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:58,029
Ľudia, som v pohode.

101
00:05:58,529 --> 00:05:59,899
Som šťastná.

102
