Kto ste?

150
00:09:21,570 --> 00:09:22,870
Kto ste?

151
00:09:23,169 --> 00:09:26,139
Prečo ma obťažujete?

152
00:09:33,379 --> 00:09:35,679
Čo? Zasa ty?

153
00:09:40,450 --> 00:09:43,820
Prečo ste taká hlučná, 
keď ste opitá?

154
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,860
Choďte domov.

155
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:49,860
Prečo? Hej!

156
00:09:49,929 --> 00:09:51,559
Otoč sa.

157
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:55,070
Pozri sa na mňa.

158
00:09:58,169 --> 00:10:00,370
Čo ťa je do toho? Čo?

159
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,009
Čo ťa je do toho, že plačem...

160
00:10:03,009 --> 00:10:04,409
alebo som hlučná?

161
00:10:04,809 --> 00:10:07,139
A či si dávam do rezancov vajce...

162
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,610
Keď sú rezance skoro hotové...

163
00:10:09,610 --> 00:10:11,250
pridajte do nich vajce.

164
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:12,779
Dodá im to skvelú chuť.

165
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:15,049
- Čo to je? 
- Moje číslo.

166
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:16,789
Len si hľadám brigádu.

167
00:10:16,789 --> 00:10:18,789
Ponukám rôzne služby.

168
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:21,559
Aha, už viem.

169
00:10:22,059 --> 00:10:23,059
Tá bankovka.

170
00:10:24,429 --> 00:10:27,230
Kam ideš? Včera si ma chcel...

171
00:10:27,230 --> 00:10:28,470
podviesť s tým eurom.

172
00:10:28,470 --> 00:10:29,870
Idem domov. Prečo?

173
00:10:30,269 --> 00:10:31,440
"Domov"?

174
00:10:32,570 --> 00:10:35,669
Kde bývaš? Tadiaľto sa ide ku mne.

175
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,980
Mali by ste prestať piť.

176
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:39,779
Nie ste jediná, 
čo býva týmto smerom.

177
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,220
Kam ideš?

178
00:10:48,389 --> 00:10:49,490
Stoj!

179
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:51,320
Ku mne domov nepôjdeš!

180
00:10:56,090 --> 00:10:57,960
Práve si sa uškrnul?

181
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:05,470
Fajn, len sa na mne smej!

182
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,710
Uškŕňaj sa!

183
00:11:09,370 --> 00:11:14,149
Zaslúžim si to.

184
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:16,950
Totálne si to zaslúžim.

185
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:24,220
Som totiž úbožiačka.

186
00:11:37,899 --> 00:11:40,039
Nikto si nezaslúži...

187
00:11:40,909 --> 00:11:42,539
aby sa na ňom uškŕňali.

188
